{"tid":2213494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"數十間網媒發表聯署聲明：反對警方自行篩選媒體","createTime":"2020-09-22T14:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T14:54:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2dedef391943d7770ede1499b9d3dc1c530acd8","tid":2213494,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"數十間網媒發表聯署聲明，反對警方自行篩選媒體，表明會繼續採訪<br />\n<br />\n有本身是獨立記者的大學講師質疑，警方以機構定義記者身份，是走回頭路。<br />\n<br />\n有立法會議員說，基本法保障新聞自由，如果傳媒採訪受新修訂影響，相信會受到法律挑戰。"},{"pid":"1db8bd88635f10f23491cd9080e7b61f44221e75","tid":2213494,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551064-20200922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551064-20200922.htm&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2yK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=c9047124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551064-20200922.htm&h=193b85a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551064-20200922.htm</a>"},{"pid":"50f08548fd805b5169a471480230bed2c29d7a63","tid":2213494,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654b8a5b0eca9cbba85ba5b94ad515dda85404cf","tid":2213494,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b6aecd21a70cfce4953e5119361ac0f87e93b2a3","tid":2213494,"uid":226515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:53:30.000Z","msg":"倒退<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a86bd88d0d0d18949931335ef2faa3bad5f5d0","tid":2213494,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"點解到左今時今日仲用【反對】呢d咁被動既用詞<br />\n<br />\n記者既採訪權同警察執行職務時既櫂力均受法律及憲法保障 <br />\n<br />\n既然同等地位既權利被某一方無理剥削，好應該改用更強硬既措詞，即係【譴責】"}]}